title: Le Veg Table
description: The Sole Hotel's restaurant (vegetarian) which is also open to the public. You access the restaurant via the hotel and is located on the 4th floor (top floor with some view of the city). No elevator. Offers breakfast, pizza and snacks until 2:00 pm and after 6:00 pm a small variety of Italian (pizza, pasta) and a larger variety of Indian dishes. Vegans please inquire.
